        "description": "Screw and rod geometry must be derived from CMM measurements of production hardware with tolerances documented. Material property uncertainty bounds (±1 sigma) must be propagated through the model for at least the two most sensitivity-ranked inputs as identified by a documented parameter sensitivity study."
