      "rationale": "Screw and rod geometry was taken from nominal CAD with no CMM measurement of test specimens. A parameter sensitivity study was initiated but only completed for rod diameter; screw thread root radius and UHMWPE block modulus were not included. Uncertainty bounds on material properties were not formally propagated — a single nominal material parameter set was used across all ensemble runs. Achieved Gradation 2; required Gradation 3. This shortfall is a primary contributor to the Not-accepted decision."
