      },
      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison performed using the ASME V&V 40 E/uval metric for all three primary QoIs. Pre-specified acceptance threshold E/uval < 1.96 documented in the validation plan prior to result unblinding. Results: stiffness E/uval=1.71 (pass), yield force E/uval=1.88 (pass), force at 40 mm E/uval=1.43 (pass). All three QoIs pass the pre-specified acceptance criterion. Gradation 3 met."
